quizOMania Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 18 Feb, 2024

This Privacy Policy describes how LittleMaster ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares information in connection with your use of our Android application quizOMania (the "App").

Information Collection and Use

Personal Information:

We may collect and store information that you voluntarily provide when using the App, such as your name, email address, and any other information you choose to provide.
Automatically Collected Information:

We may automatically collect certain information when you use the App, including but not limited to your device type, operating system version, unique device identifiers, IP address, and usage information.
Location Information:

The App may collect and use your precise location data if you grant the necessary permissions. This information is used to provide location-based services within the App.
How We Use Your Information

Providing and Improving the App:

We use the information collected to operate, maintain, and improve the App, as well as to develop new features and functionality.
Communications:

We may use your email address to send you important updates or information related to the App. You can opt-out of receiving these communications.
Analytics:

We may use third-party analytics tools to analyze usage patterns and optimize the App.
Information Sharing

Third-Party Service Providers:

We may share your information with third-party service providers who help us operate and improve the App.
Legal Compliance:

We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to valid legal requests.
Security

We take reasonable measures to help protect the information collected from loss, theft, misuse, and unauthorized access.

Your Choices

You may opt-out of certain data collection and communications by adjusting your device settings or contacting us directly.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will be made available in the App.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at garg.shivam@gmail.com.
